replies.body:
1. If your good at last hitting its now worth double the AP it used to be.
2. Yes, covering more range means you can poke better with it. if you miss all the time, your shit at pokeing with skill shots and need to play point and click champions. they are not inherently better at poke, just easier.  Personally for mid lane poke I love {{champion:115}} {{champion:101}} 
3. His laneing was made better for this change, it scales him into late game faster. Lane phase is all about getting to your power spikes.
